.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: black, purple, brown, coral, ebony
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, turkish, australian, spanish
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-iced-7up, almond-iced-7up, iced-7up, 7up, juice
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blackmaster, tiparillo, oliveros, cain, game
5 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, guinea-pig, rat, hedgehog
1. the nigerian is the person who likes brown
2. the swedish is the owner of the guinea-pig
3. the pakistani is the person drinking 7up
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes coral
5. the person who likes purple is the person drinking almond-iced-7up
6. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the rabbit
7. the person who likes ebony is the tiparillo-smoker
8. the person drinking iced-7up is in the middle
9. the australian is on the far left
10. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard
11. the owner of the hedgehogs is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker
12. the blackmaster-smoker is the person drinking soy-iced-7up
13. the turkish is the cain-smoker
14. the australian is on the left or right of the person who likes black
15. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking juice

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    ebony	|     black	|      brown	|     purple	|     coral	|
| Nationality	|   australian	|    pakistani	|    nigerian	|    turkish	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     lizard	|    hedgehog	|     rabbit	|     rat	|      guinea-pig	|
| Beverage	|    juice	|     7up	|     iced-7up	|    almond-iced-7up	|      soy-iced-7up	|
| Cigar		|   tiparillo	|    game	|  oliveros	|    cain	|   blackmaster	|
